#. plugin:google-analytics:summary
#: 
msgid "Google Analytics 4 (GA4) tracks how users interact with ChurchCRM, providing insights into page views, user engagement, and feature usage."
msgstr "Google Analytics 4 (GA4) ተጠቃሚዎች ከ ChurchCRM ጋር እንዴት እንደሚገናኙ ይከታተላል፣ ስለ ገጽ ዕይታዎች፣ የተጠቃሚ ተሳትፎ እና የባህሪ አጠቃቀም ግንዛቤዎች ይሰጣል።"

#. plugin:google-analytics:link:0:label
#: 
msgid "Google Analytics Help"
msgstr "Google Analytics እገዛ"

#. plugin:google-analytics:section:2:content
#: 
msgid "Google Analytics collects anonymized usage data. No personal information from ChurchCRM records is sent to Google. Consider adding a privacy notice to your church's data policy."
msgstr "Google Analytics ስም-አልባ የአጠቃቀም ዳታ ይሰበስባል። ከ ChurchCRM ሪኮርዶች ምንም ግል መረጃ ወደ Google አይላክም። ለቤተ ክርስቲያናቸው የዳታ ፖሊሲ የግልዊነት ማስታወሻ ማከልን ያስቡ።"

#. plugin:gravatar:summary
