#. plugin:gravatar:section:2:content
#: 
msgid "Gravatar works by converting email addresses into a hash (MD5). The actual email address is never sent to Gravatar's servers - only the hash is used to look up the image."
msgstr "Gravatar የኢሜይል አድራሻዎችን ወደ ሀሽ (MD5) በመቀየር ይሰራል። ትክክለኛው የኢሜይል አድራሻ ወደ Gravatar አገልጋዮች ፈጽሞ አይላክም - ምስሉን ለፈለጎ ሀሽ ብቻ ጥቅም ላይ ይውላል።"

#: 
msgid "Hide Latitude/Longitude"
msgstr "ኬክሮስ/ኦሮምን ደብቅ"

#: 
msgid "Hide Person Address"
msgstr "የሰው አድራሻ ደብቅ"

#. plugin:gravatar:section:0:title
#. plugin:openlp:section:1:title
#: 
msgid "How it works"
msgstr "እንዴት እንደሚሰራ"

