#. plugin:external-backup:section:5:title
#: 
msgid "Supported Services"
msgstr "የሚደገፉ አገልግሎቶች"

#. plugin:external-backup:section:4:title
#: 
msgid "Testing Connection"
msgstr "ግንኙነት መሞከር"

#. plugin:custom-links:section:0:content
#: 
msgid "The Custom Menu Links plugin allows administrators to add external links to the navigation menu. When enabled, a 'Links' menu appears in the sidebar containing all configured links."
msgstr "ብጁ ምናሌ ማገናኛዎች ፕለጊን አስተዳዳሪዎች ወደ ናቪጌሽን ምናሌ ውጫዊ ማገናኛዎችን እንዲጨምሩ ያስችላቸዋል። ሲነቃ፣ ሁሉም የተዋቀሩ ማገናኛዎችን ያካተተ 'ማገናኛዎች' ምናሌ ጎን ላይ ይታያል።"

#. plugin:external-backup:section:0:content
#: 
msgid "The External Backup plugin allows you to automatically backup your ChurchCRM database to WebDAV-compatible cloud storage services. This includes popular services like Nextcloud, ownCloud, or any server supporting WebDAV protocol."
msgstr "ውጫዊ ምትኬ ፕለጊን የ ChurchCRM ዳታቤዝዎን ወደ WebDAV-ተኳሃኝ ክላውድ ማከማቻ አገልግሎቶች ራስ-ሰር ለምትኬ ያስችልዎታል። ይህ Nextcloud፣ ownCloud ወይም WebDAV ፕሮቶኮልን ደጋፊ ማንኛውም አገልጋይ ጨምሮ ታዋቂ አገልግሎቶችን ያካትታል።"

#. plugin:openlp:section:3:content
#: 
msgid "The default OpenLP port is 4316. Your server URL will typically be: http://192.168.x.x:4316 where 192.168.x.x is the IP address of the computer running OpenLP. You can find this in OpenLP under Tools → Open Service Manager."
msgstr "ነባሪ OpenLP ወደብ 4316 ነው። አገልጋዩ URL ብዙ ጊዜ ይህ ይሆናል: http://192.168.x.x:4316 192.168.x.x OpenLP ያሄደበት ኮምፒዩተር IP አድራሻ ነው። ይህን በ OpenLP ስር Tools → Open Service Manager ከፍተው ማግኘት ይችላሉ።"

#: 
msgid "The month that starts your organization's fiscal year"
msgstr "የድርጅቱ የፋይናንስ ዓመት የሚጀምርበት ወር"

#. plugin:vonage:section:0:content
#: 
msgid "This plugin is currently used for Kiosk Check-in Notifications. When a child is checked into a Sunday School class via the kiosk system, an SMS can be sent to notify parents or guardians."
msgstr "ይህ ፕለጊን በአሁኑ ጊዜ ለኪዮስክ ቼክ-ኢን ማሳወቂያዎች ጥቅም ላይ ይውላል። አንድ ልጅ በኪዮስክ ሥርዓት አማካኝነት ወደ ሰንበት ትምህርት ቤት ክፍል ሲቀጥር፣ ወላጆቻቸውን ወይም አሳዳጊዎቻቸውን ለማሳወቅ SMS ሊላክ ይችላል።"

#. plugin:openlp:section:0:content
#: 
msgid "This plugin is currently used for Kiosk Check-in Notifications. When a child is checked into a Sunday School class via the kiosk system, an alert can be sent to the OpenLP projector display to notify parents or volunteers."
msgstr "ይህ ፕለጊን በአሁኑ ጊዜ ለኪዮስክ ቼክ-ኢን ማሳወቂያዎች ጥቅም ላይ ይውላል። አንድ ልጅ በኪዮስክ ሥርዓት አማካኝነት ወደ ሰንበት ትምህርት ቤት ክፍል ሲቀጥር፣ ወላጆቻቸውን ወይም በጎ ፈቃደኞቻቸውን ለማሳወቅ ወደ OpenLP ፕሮጀክተር ማሳያ ማንቂያ ሊላክ ይችላል።"

#. plugin:mailchimp:section:4:content
#: 
msgid "This plugin transmits email addresses to MailChimp servers. Ensure you have appropriate consent from your members before syncing their information to third-party services like MailChimp."
msgstr "ይህ ፕለጊን የኢሜይል አድራሻዎችን ወደ MailChimp አገልጋዮች ይልካል። የአባሎቻቸውን መረጃ ወደ MailChimp ያሉ ሦስተኛ ወገን አገልግሎቶች ከማመሳሰልዎ በፊት ከአባሎቻቸው ተገቢ ፈቃድ ማግኘታቸውን ያረጋግጡ።"

#. plugin:custom-links:section:1:content
#: 
msgid "To add a new link:\n"
"1. Go to the Links menu in the sidebar and click 'Manage Links'\n"
"2. Enter a display name (2-50 characters)\n"
"3. Enter the full URL (must start with http:// or https://)\n"
"4. Click 'Add Link'\n"
"\n"
"The link will immediately appear in the Links menu."
msgstr "አዲስ ማገናኛ ለመጨመር:\n"
"1. ወደ ጎን ምናሌ ውስጥ ያለው ማገናኛዎች ምናሌ ሂደው 'ማገናኛዎችን ያስተዳድሩ' ን ጠቅ ያድርጉ\n"
"2. ማሳያ ስም ያስገቡ (2-50 ቁምፊዎች)\n"
"3. ሙሉ URL ያስገቡ (http:// ወይም https:// ብለው መጀመር አለበት)\n"
"4. 'ማገናኛ ጨምር' ን ጠቅ ያድርጉ\n"
"\n"
"ማገናኛ ወዲያውኑ በማገናኛዎች ምናሌ ውስጥ ይታያል።"

#. plugin:external-backup:section:1:content
#: 
msgid "To configure external backups:\n"
"1. Go to Admin > Plugins and find 'External Backup (WebDAV)'\n"
"2. Click the settings icon to expand the configuration panel\n"
"3. Enter your WebDAV endpoint URL (e.g., https://cloud.example.com/remote.php/dav/files/username/backups/)\n"
"4. Enter your username and password\n"
"5. Optionally set an auto-backup interval in hours\n"
"6. Save your settings"
msgstr "ውጫዊ ምትኬዎችን ለማዋቀር:\n"
"1. ወደ አስተዳደር > ፕለጊኖች ሂደው 'ውጫዊ ምትኬ (WebDAV)' ን ያግኙ\n"
"2. የማዋቀሪያ ፓነልን ለማስፋፋት የቅንጅቶች አዶን ጠቅ ያድርጉ\n"
"3. WebDAV ኤንድፖይንት URL ያስገቡ (ለምሳሌ፣ https://cloud.example.com/remote.php/dav/files/username/backups/)\n"
"4. ተጠቃሚ ስምና የሚስጥር ቃሉን ያስገቡ\n"
"5. በፈቃደኝነት ራስ-ሰር ምትኬ ክፍተትን በሰዓቶች ያስቀምጡ\n"
"6. ቅንጅቶቻቸውን ያስቀምጡ"

#. plugin:mailchimp:section:0:content
#: 
msgid "To use MailChimp Integration, you need a MailChimp account and an API key.\n"
"\n"
"1. Log in to your MailChimp account\n"
"2. Go to Account > Extras > API Keys\n"
"3. Create a new API key or copy an existing one\n"
"4. Enter the API key in the plugin settings"
msgstr "MailChimp ውህደትን ለመጠቀም፣ MailChimp መለያ እና API ቁልፍ ያስፈልጋሉ።\n"
"\n"
"1. ወደ MailChimp መለያዎ ይግቡ\n"
"2. ወደ መለያ > ተጨማሪዎች > API ቁልፎች ይሂዱ\n"
"3. አዲስ API ቁልፍ ይፍጠሩ ወይም ነባሩን ይቅዱ\n"
"4. API ቁልፍን በፕለጊን ቅንጅቶች ውስጥ ያስገቡ"

#. plugin:openlp:section:5:title
#: 
msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr "ችግር ፈቺ"

#. plugin:vonage:section:4:title
#: 
msgid "Troubleshooting - Invalid Sender ID"
msgstr "ችግር ፈቺ - ልክ ያልሆነ ልኳ መታወቂያ"

#. plugin:vonage:section:5:title
#: 
msgid "Troubleshooting - Messages Not Delivered"
msgstr "ችግር ፈቺ - መልዕክቶች አልተላኩም"

#. plugin:vonage:section:3:title
#: 
msgid "Troubleshooting - SMS Not Sending"
msgstr "ችግር ፈቺ - ኤስኤምኤስ አይልክም"

#: 
msgid "Upgrade Settings"
msgstr "ዝመና ቅንጅቶች"

#. plugin:custom-links:section:4:title
#: 
msgid "Use Cases"
msgstr "አጠቃቀም ሁኔታዎች"

#. plugin:vonage:link:0:label
#: 
msgid "Vonage Dashboard"
msgstr "Vonage ዳሽቦርድ"

#. plugin:vonage:link:2:label
#: 
msgid "Vonage Pricing"
msgstr "Vonage ዋጋ"

#. plugin:vonage:link:1:label
#: 
msgid "Vonage SMS API Documentation"
msgstr "Vonage SMS API ሰነዶች"

#. plugin:vonage:summary
#: 
msgid "Vonage SMS enables text message notifications for ChurchCRM using the Vonage API (formerly Nexmo). Send SMS alerts to parents when their child checks in via the kiosk system."
msgstr "Vonage SMS የ Vonage API (ቀደም ሲል Nexmo) ተጠቅሞ ለ ChurchCRM የጽሑፍ መልዕክት ማሳወቂያዎችን ያስችላል። ልጃቸው በኪዮስክ ሥርዓት ሲቀጥር ወላጆቻቸውን SMS ማንቂያ ይላኩ።"

#. plugin:vonage:section:6:content
#: 
msgid "Vonage charges per SMS sent. Pricing varies by destination country. See the Vonage pricing page for current rates. New accounts receive free trial credit for testing."
msgstr "Vonage ለሚላክ SMS ያስከፍላል። ዋጋ ወደ ቀጣዩ ሀገር ይለያያል። የአሁኑ ዋጋዎችን ለማወቅ የ Vonage ዋጋ ገጽ ይመልከቱ። አዲስ መለያዎች ለሙከራ ነጻ የሙከራ ክሬዲት ይቀበላሉ።"

#. plugin:google-analytics:section:1:title
#: 
msgid "What Gets Tracked"
msgstr "ምን እንደሚከታተል"

#. plugin:mailchimp:section:3:content
#: 
msgid "When MailChimp is configured, a 'MailChimp' tab appears on Person view pages showing:\n"
"\n"
"- Email subscription status across all lists\n"
"- Which lists the person is subscribed to\n"
"- Subscription statistics"
msgstr "MailChimp ሲዋቀር፣ 'MailChimp' ትር ሰው ዕይታ ገጾች ላይ ይታያል:\n"
"\n"
"- ሁሉም ዝርዝሮች ላይ ያለ የኢሜይል ደንበኝነት ሁኔታ\n"
"- ሰዉ የተቀጠረባቸው ዝርዝሮች\n"
"- የደንበኝነት ስታቲስቲክስ"

#. plugin:gravatar:section:0:content
#: 
msgid "When a member doesn't have an uploaded photo, ChurchCRM checks if they have a Gravatar associated with their email address. If a Gravatar exists, it displays that image. If not, the configured default image style is used."
msgstr "አባሉ ፎቶ ያልጫኑ ሲሆን፣ ChurchCRM ከኢሜይል አድራሻቸው ጋር የተያያዘ Gravatar ያለ ስለ መሆናቸው ይፈትሻል። Gravatar ካለ፣ ያ ምስል ይታያል። ካልሆነ፣ የተዋቀረው ነባሪ ምስል ዘይቤ ጥቅም ላይ ይውላል።"

#. plugin:external-backup:section:2:content
#: 
msgid "When auto-backup is enabled (interval > 0 hours), ChurchCRM will automatically create and upload a full database backup at the specified interval. The backup runs as part of normal page loads, so the system must have regular user activity to trigger backups.\n"
"\n"
"Recommended intervals:\n"
"- Daily backup: 24 hours\n"
"- Twice daily: 12 hours\n"
"- Weekly: 168 hours"
msgstr "ራስ-ሰር ምትኬ ሲነቃ (ክፍተት > 0 ሰዓቶች)፣ ChurchCRM በተጠቀሰው ክፍተት ሙሉ የዳታቤዝ ምትኬ ራስ-ሰር ይፈጥርና ይጭናል። ምትኬ ተለምዷዊ ገጽ ጭነቶች አካል ሆኖ ይሄዳል፣ ስለዚህ ምትኬዎችን ለማስጀመር ሥርዓቱ መደበኛ የተጠቃሚ እንቅስቃሴ ሊኖረው ይገባል።\n"
"\n"
"የሚመከሩ ክፍተቶች:\n"
"- ዕለታዊ ምትኬ: 24 ሰዓቶች\n"
"- ቀኑ ሁለት ጊዜ: 12 ሰዓቶች\n"
"- ሳምንታዊ: 168 ሰዓቶች"

#. plugin:openlp:section:1:content
#: 
msgid "When enabled and configured, ChurchCRM sends alert messages to your OpenLP server using the API v2 endpoint (POST /api/v2/plugins/alerts). These alerts appear as overlay notifications on your projected display."
msgstr "ሲነቃ እና ሲዋቀር፣ ChurchCRM ማስጠንቀቂያ መልዕክቶችን ወደ OpenLP አገልጋይዎ API v2 ኤንድፖይንት ተጠቅሞ (POST /api/v2/plugins/alerts) ይልካል። እነዚህ ማስጠንቀቂያዎች በተጣለ ማሳያዎ ላይ ማደራጃ ማሳወቂያዎች ሆነው ይታያሉ።"

#: 
msgid "When enabled, hides the address field for people not assigned to a family"
msgstr "ሲነቃ፣ ለቤተሰብ ያልተሰጡ ሰዎች የአድራሻ ሜዳን ይደብቃል"

#: 
msgid "When enabled, hides the latitude/longitude fields in the Family Editor. Geocoding still runs in the background."
msgstr "ሲነቃ፣ በቤተሰብ አዘጋጅ ውስጥ ያሉ የኬክሮስ/ኬንትሮስ ሜዳዎችን ይደብቃል። ጂኦኮዲንግ አሁንም ዳራ ላይ ይሰራል።"

#. plugin:external-backup:section:3:content
#: 
msgid "You can also trigger a manual backup at any time:\n"
"1. Go to the External Backup settings page (Plugins > External Backup)\n"
"2. Select backup type (Database Only or Full Backup)\n"
"3. Click 'Backup to WebDAV Now'\n"
"\n"
"Database Only backups are smaller and faster. Full backups include uploaded photos."
msgstr "እንዲሁም በማንኛውም ጊዜ ሰው-ሰራሽ ምትኬ ማስጀመር ይችላሉ:\n"
"1. ወደ ውጫዊ ምትኬ ቅንጅቶች ገጽ (ፕለጊኖች > ውጫዊ ምትኬ) ሂዱ\n"
"2. ምትኬ ዓይነት ይምረጡ (ዳታቤዝ ብቻ ወይም ሙሉ ምትኬ)\n"
"3. 'አሁን ወደ WebDAV ምትኬ አድርግ' ን ጠቅ ያድርጉ\n"
"\n"
"ዳታቤዝ ብቻ ምትኬዎች ትንሽ እና ፈጣን ናቸው። ሙሉ ምትኬዎች የተጫኑ ፎቶዎችን ያካትታሉ።"

#. plugin:google-analytics:section:1:content
#: 
